 *
 * rseq MCU common overlay.
 *
 * Board-specific wiring lives in boards/<board>.overlay. Chip bus/address
 * selection is supplied by the rseq script.
 *
 * Keep transport selection in boards/<board>.overlay via /chosen
 * rseq,transport. This file is intentionally empty so boards without target
 * USB device wiring are not forced to instantiate a CDC-ACM node.
 */
